# Media — Logo Single-Shot Prompt Manifest
# Maps business identity inputs into a curated logo-generation prompt.

template_type: KnowAct
name: media_logo_single_shot
version: "1.0.0"
description: "Generate a logo from business identity inputs — name, industry, style, colors"
model: "FA/flux-pro/v1"
parameters:
  - name: name
    type: string
    required: true
    description: "Business or group name"
  - name: tagline
    type: string
    required: false
    description: "Optional tagline or motto"
  - name: industry
    type: string
    required: false
    description: "Industry context (tech, food, legal, creative, etc.)"
  - name: style
    type: enum
    values: [minimal, modern, playful, corporate, vintage, luxury, tech, handmade, bold, elegant]
    default: minimal
    description: "Visual style direction"
  - name: palette
    type: string
    required: false
    description: "Hex colors (e.g., '#1a1a2e,#e94560,#ffffff') or named palette (monochrome, warm, cool, earth, neon)"
  - name: logo_type
    type: enum
    values: [wordmark, lettermark, emblem, abstract, combination, mascot]
    default: wordmark
    description: "Type of logo mark"
---
Design a professional logo for a {% if industry %}{{ industry }}{% else %}business{% endif %} called "{{ name }}"{% if tagline %}, with the tagline "{{ tagline }}"{% endif %}.

Style: {{ style }}
Logo type: {{ logo_type }}
{% if palette %}
Color palette: {{ palette }}
{% endif %}

Requirements:
- Clean, scalable vector-style design
- Works in monochrome as well as color
- No realistic photography or 3D rendering — flat or subtly shaded illustration style
- Solid or gradient background preferred — no transparent/checkerboard
- No text artifacts, garbled letters, or misspelled words
- High contrast, legible at small sizes
- Professional, not clip-art

Return a single logo image.
